        {
          "id": "498a1fc73182_19",
          "href": null,
          "name": "9b56",
          "text": "Regenerating the biosphere is an urgent necessity and could turn into a shared vision big enough to bring humanity together in all its diversity. We are called to be part of a maturation process of our own species and step into responsible membership of the community of life.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 85,
              "href": "https://medium.com/@designforsustainability/the-role-of-vision-in-design-6ff39ed602c0",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 72,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            },
            {
              "end": 194,
              "href": "https://medium.com/insurge-intelligence/integrating-economy-and-ecology-with-wisdom-fd4eeaa376c7",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 176,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "498a1fc73182_20",
          "href": null,
          "name": "23b7",
          "text": "The 21st Century will be the century of ecosystem and Earth regeneration, otherwise the 22nd Century might see a greatly impoversihed planet without us.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
